class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/developer\">开发者路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">Agent 开发</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Agent 开发</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">Agent 开发实战</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->110分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>开发者路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/agent/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/agent/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/agent/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>记忆系统设计</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-blue-700\">Agent 的三重记忆系统</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded-lg border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-blue-600\">① 工作记忆（Immediate Memory）</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">保存当前对话和执行状态，容量有限但访问快速</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">实现：消息队列、状态字典、Token 管理</p></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded-lg border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-green-600\">② 短期记忆（RAG Memory）</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">通过向量检索调用知识库，提供丰富信息</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">实现：向量数据库、语义检索算法</p></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-white rounded-lg border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-purple-600\">③ 长期记忆（Long-term Memory）</p><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">持久化的用户偏好和学习经验，跨会话积累</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1\">实现：数据库存储、KV 存储、总结提炼机制</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">记忆管理系统架构</h4><div class=\"bg-white p-3 rounded border text-sm font-mono\"><pre>class MemoryManager:\n    def __init__(self):\n        self.working_memory = []     # 工作记忆\n        self.vector_store = None     # 短期记忆（RAG）\n        self.long_term_store = DB()  # 长期记忆\n\n    def add(self, content, type=&quot;working&quot;):\n        if type == &quot;working&quot;:\n            self.working_memory.append(content)\n        elif type == &quot;long_term&quot;:\n            self.long_term_store.save(content)\n\n    def retrieve(self, query, max_tokens=4000):\n        # 1. 优先工作记忆\n        result = self.working_memory\n\n        # 2. 补充短期记忆（直到达到 Token 限制）\n        remaining = max_tokens - count_tokens(result)\n        if remaining &gt; 0:\n            rag_items = self.vector_store.search(query, k=5)\n            result.extend(rag_items)\n\n        return result</pre></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>工具调用框架</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-green-700\">标准化的工具接口</h4><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-3 rounded font-mono text-sm\"><pre>class Tool:\n    def __init__(self, name, description):\n        self.name = name\n        self.description = description\n        self.parameters = {}  # 参数 Schema\n        self.cost = 0.01      # 调用成本\n\n    async def execute(self, **kwargs):\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;执行工具，返回结果&quot;&quot;&quot;\n        raise NotImplementedError\n\n    def to_schema(self):\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;返回工具的 JSON Schema&quot;&quot;&quot;\n        return {\n            &quot;type&quot;: &quot;function&quot;,\n            &quot;function&quot;: {\n                &quot;name&quot;: self.name,\n                &quot;description&quot;: self.description,\n                &quot;parameters&quot;: self.parameters\n            }\n        }\n\n# 工具示例\nclass SearchFilesTool(Tool):\n    def __init__(self):\n        super().__init__(\n            name=&quot;search_files&quot;,\n            description=&quot;搜索文件内容，找出匹配关键词的文件&quot;\n        )\n        self.parameters = {\n            &quot;type&quot;: &quot;object&quot;,\n            &quot;properties&quot;: {\n                &quot;query&quot;: {&quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;, &quot;description&quot;: &quot;搜索关键词&quot;},\n                &quot;path&quot;: {&quot;type&quot;: &quot;string&quot;, &quot;description&quot;: &quot;搜索路径&quot;}\n            },\n            &quot;required&quot;: [&quot;query&quot;]\n        }\n\n    async def execute(self, query, path=&quot;.&quot;):\n        # 实现文件搜索逻辑\n        results = grep(query, path)\n        return f&quot;找到 {len(results)} 个匹配文件&quot;</pre></div></div><div class=\"bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-2 text-purple-700\">工具选择策略</h4><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">Agent 如何知道该调用哪个工具？使用向量相似度匹配工具描述：</p><div class=\"bg-white p-2 rounded border text-xs mt-2\"><p>用户意图：&quot;查询当前股票价格&quot;</p><p>工具描述相似度：</p><p>  - search_files: 0.23 (不相关)</p><p>  - get_weather: 0.31 (不相关)</p><p>  <span class=\"text-green-600\">- get_stock_price: 0.89 (最相关 ✓)</span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">3</span>任务分解算法</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"bg-orange-50 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3 text-orange-700\">将复杂任务分解为可执行步骤</h4><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"p-2 bg-white rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">1. 递归分解（Recursive Decomposition）</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">不断将任务拆分直到成为原子操作</p><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-xs mt-1\"><p>任务：&quot;开发一个用户系统&quot;</p><p>→ 开发注册功能, 开发登录功能, 开发权限管理</p><p>  → 设计数据库, 编写API, 前端页面</p></div></div><div class=\"p-2 bg-white rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">2. 依赖图分析（Dependency Graph）</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">识别任务间的依赖关系，生成执行顺序</p><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-2 rounded text-xs mt-1\"><p>注册功能 → 数据库设计 → 登录功能</p><p>（登录需要先有数据库）</p></div></div><div class=\"p-2 bg-white rounded border\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm\">3. 优先级排序</p><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-600\">根据重要性和紧急度安排顺序</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">任务分解代码示例</h4><div class=\"font-mono text-xs\"><pre>class TaskDecomposer:\n    def decompose(self, goal, tools):\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;将目标分解为可执行的任务图&quot;&quot;&quot;\n        prompt = f&quot;&quot;&quot;\n        目标：{goal}\n        可用工具：{[t.name for t in tools]}\n\n        请将目标分解为具体步骤。\n        格式：\n        步骤1：[行动描述]，使用工具：[工具名]\n        步骤2：...\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;\n\n        steps = await llm.generate(prompt)\n        return self.parse_steps(steps)\n\n    def parse_steps(self, text):\n        &quot;&quot;&quot;解析生成的步骤&quot;&quot;&quot;\n        # 使用正则或结构化提取\n        # 返回任务列表：[{&quot;action&quot;: &quot;...&quot;, &quot;tool&quot;: &quot;...&quot;}, ...]\n        pass</pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/developer\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->开发者路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[30824,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"Providers\\\"]\\n3:I[87161,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[40715,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[78691,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[30470,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n9:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\nc:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\ne:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\n10:I[92691,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.6dsdn